XL Group Plc (XL) , the insurer led by
Chief Executive Officer Mike McGavick, built a team to provide
crisis coverage for events including war, terrorism, kidnappings
and product recalls.  The team will be led in New York by Denise Balan, who
previously worked for  American International Group Inc. (AIG) , Dublin-based XL said today in a statement distributed by PR Newswire.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Noah Buhayar in New York at 
